// https://www.khronos.org/registry/webgl/specs/1.0/#6.13
// https://github.com/KhronosGroup/WebGL/blob/0d3201f5f7ec3c0060bc1f04077461541f1987b9/conformance-suites/1.0.3/conformance/misc/webgl-specific.html#L56
